{"tid":2477400,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"90後月供六合彩兩年 突然置業","createTime":"2021-04-06T09:22:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T23:49:35.000Z","uid":81028,"like":99,"dislike":463,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"9533c7a71bf129b28cb8bc55304567fcf3f0d44e","tid":2477400,"uid":81028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T09:22:32.000Z","msg":"好多上班族都會把部分薪水用投資，希望透過資本市場自己的資產增值。月供股票，基金，保險是最常見的投資方法。<br />\n<br />\n最近香港開始有很多90後我月供六合彩，希望透過博彩市場，更快實現自己的理財目標。<br />\n<br />\n花名D 的上班族，性格節儉，平時和朋友外出吃飯都會就住就住。奢侈品更甚少購買，對上一台電話已經用了4年，去年壞了，才更換三星的平價手機。在朋友眼中的生活非常寒酸。最近和朋友見面。發現D 他已經出入好貴的酒店staycation，一晚成幾千元。他和另外一半也已經有房子和車位。也購買了過萬元的相機。出街食飯每餐都接近1千。朋友都很難以置信D 最近的改變。之後朋友們想起D 之前有提及他月供六合彩的計劃後，一切謎底解開。<br />\n<br />\n至於如何月供六合彩，如果過20個好評，就出文教學。"},{"pid":"04092c1b34a7c0edfb5d0616312359cadad35c0e","tid":2477400,"uid":59030,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T09:23:32.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"3fd0d8a9ac2e732afb8b89b3a3cde22a8043355c","tid":2477400,"uid":329977,"like":127,"dislike":13,"score":114,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T09:24:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYtVLKZT8CX5Pzpok33isKpWFDiYDo4fctJKKSqh43SDS?filename=7iodTpC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7iodTpC.gif&h=26943d78&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d2b933c2b2c0c70d57cff48161fd9965df4090e3","tid":2477400,"uid":262116,"like":89,"dislike":4,"score":85,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T09:29:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPTLtpybDvb3MFVsDdeJNRsj3SiNLutADoLPr1tj5FiRh?filename=KcbV6Ma.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKcbV6Ma.gif&h=83c71ce6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a3d2c696c61ae3c4b2d28fbdb0d3bab0997d192a","tid":2477400,"uid":266336,"like":281,"dislike":4,"score":277,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T09:33:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTsdixSRgdzUn9dSrr2XNqSoTZqMNSsSYukRSSKSnQsev?filename=hTmZO0f.jpg\" data-thumbnail